What Is Your Battle Cry?

Sprinting over the hotel lobby, wielding buzzsaw hand extensions, cometh Sugaroverspite! And she gives a gutteral roar:

"For the love of beatings, skulls will be fucked for Satan!!"

Find out!
Enter username:
Are you a girl, or a guy ?

created by beatings : powered by monkeys

I have a cell phone!  ^_^

MWAHAHAHAHAHAHA!

That is all.

This is a warning from me.

Right now I am pmsing.

I hate EVERYONE.  The only people this does not apply to are:

1. People in foreign countries
2. People I have not spoken to, about, or encountered in any way in the last six hours
3. People who are dead
4. People who I don't know about.
5. Shanda

This does not exclude relatives.  You know who you are.

Any attempts to speak to me will be rebuffed, questions and requests denied.  I will answer no just to spite you.  I will refuse to cooperate or even listen to you.

I will throw things because I can, eat chocolate because I can, and hate you... because I can.

I am a bitch, and nothing you do will placate me.

Some of you deserve this right now; most of you don't.

My advice is to stay far away until I chill out and stop foaming at the mouth.

R

Any second now... I will summon the will power to move.

Next step... caring.

In the far future, there may be food, and possibly working.

But for now, contemplation.

R

Ano...

Kyo no shuumatsu ha totemo muzukashi ka na...

Scott no paati ha ii to omou demo paati no ato de kurabu ni imashita... isogashisugimasu yo.  Watashi ga kurabu de ongaku wo kitte, odotte, takusan omou koto ga suki desu.  Demo, watashi no ichiban tomodachi wa shinpai shimasu kara, watashi ga atama ga itain.  Tomodachi ha kare no mondai ga aru kara, ureshikute, okorimashita.  Sore kara, watashi mo atama ga itain deshou.

Iroirona hito ha odorimashita.

Kokoro ga itain darou.

Doushite maishuu ookii mondai morau kara hito ha odorimasu?  Ureshii ni naru ka naa...

Mou... 

Watashi ha ii koto ga aru dake... doushite sabishii?  Doushite ureshii?

Kore ha watashi no mondai ga nai... doushite shinpai shite imasu? Watashi ga kare no mondai ga arimasen ne... doushite tomodachi no kare no mondai wa watashi no mondai ni narimasu ka?

Watashi wa kare ga aru toki, mondai ha ii yo.  Demo, ima ha... urasai.

Sou ka naa...

Sarah san no mondai mo ookii ni narimasu.  Mitakunai, demo... minakuchaikemasen.

Chinmoku jikan ga hoshi naa...

Nemui yo.  Ima, omoemasen yo.
Every journal has to have a test entry, right?  Well, here is mine!  ^_~
